{{Infobox journal | title = 4OR | image = 4ORJournal.jpg | editors = Yves Crama, Michel Grabisch, Silvano Martello | discipline = [[Operations Research]], [[Decision Theory]] | abbreviation = 4OR | publisher = [[Springer Science+Business Media]] | country = | frequency = | history = 2003-present | openaccess = | license = | impact = | impact-year = | website = https://link.springer.com/journal/10288 | link1 = https://link.springer.com/journal/volumesAndIssues/10288 | link1-name = Online access | link2 = | link2-name = | JSTOR = | OCLC = | LCCN = | CODEN = | ISSN = 1619-4500 | eISSN = 1614-2411 }}
'''''4OR - A Quarterly Journal of Operations Research''''' is a [[Peer review|peer-reviewed]] [[scientific journal]] that was established in 2003 and is published by [[Springer Science+Business Media]]. It is a joint official journal of the [[Belgian Society for Operations Research|Belgian]], [[Société française de Recherche Opérationnelle et Aide à la Décision|French]], and [[Italian Operations Research Society|Italian]] Operations Research Societies. The journal publishes research papers and surveys on the theory and applications of Operations Research. The [[editor-in-chief|Editors-in-chief]] are Yves Crama ([[University of Liège]]), Michel Grabisch ([[Pantheon-Sorbonne University]]), and Silvano Martello ([[University of Bologna]]).
== Abstracting and indexing == The journal is abstracted and indexed in the following databases:<ref name=home>{{cite web |url=https://link.springer.com/journal/10288 |title=About 4OR - A Quarterly Journal of Operations Research |format= |work= |accessdate=2017-11-12}}</ref> * [[DBLP]] * [[EconLit]] * [[EBSCO Information Services]] * [[Google Scholar]] * [[International Abstracts in Operations Research]] * [[Journal Citation Reports]] * [[Mathematical Reviews]] * [[OCLC]] * [[ProQuest]] * [[Science Citation Index]] * [[SCImago Journal Rank]] * [[Scopus]] * [[Zentralblatt Math]]
According to the ''[[Journal Citation Reports]]'', the journal has a 2016 [[impact factor]] of 1.559.
