{{term|term= fugacious |content= fugacious {{anchor| fugacious}} }}
{{defn|defn= Disappearing, falling off, or withering. Compare [[#persistent|persistent]] and [[#caducous|caducous]].}}

{{term|term= funicle |content= funicle (funiculus) {{anchor|funiculus}} }}
{{defn|defn= The stalk of an [[#ovule|ovule]].}}

{{term|term= funnelform |content= [[funnelform]] }}
{{defn|defn= Having a form gradually widening from the base to apex; funnel-shaped.}}

{{term|term= furcate |content= [[furcate]] }}
{{defn|defn= Forked, usually applied to a terminal division; with two long lobes.}}

{{term|term= fused }}
{{defn|defn= Joined together.}}

{{term|term= fusiform |content= [[wikt:fusiform|fusiform]] }}
{{defn|defn= Rod-shaped and narrowing gradually from the middle towards each end; spindle-shaped.}}

