{{term|term= helicoid |content= [[helicoid]] }}
{{defn|defn= Coiled; of a [[#cymose|cymose]] inflorescence, when the branching is repeatedly on the same side (the apex is often [[#recurved|recurved]]). Compare [[#scorpioid|scorpioid]].}}

{{term|term= hemi-legume  |content= hemi-legume }}
{{defn|defn= A legume fruit in which the seed or seeds and one valve of the pod are dispersed as a unit. The valve catches the wind and blows away with the seeds, as in ''[[Acaccia tenuifolia]]'', ''[[Peltogyne paniculata]]''.}} 

{{term|term= herb |content= [[herb]] }}
