{{term|term= microsporangium }}
{{defn|defn= The smaller of two kinds of [[#sporangium|sporangium]] produced by a [[#heterospory|heterosporous]] plant, producing [[#microspore|microspores]] that contain the male [[#gametophyte|gametophyte]]. Compare [[#megasporangium|megasporangium]].}}

{{term|term= microspore |content= [[microspore]] }}
