{{term|term= microsporophyll }}
{{defn|defn= In [[#heterospory|heterosporous]] plants, a modified leaf bearing one or more [[#microsporangium|microsporangia]]. Compare [[#megasporophyll|megasporophyll]]. }}

{{term|term= microstrobilus |content= [[microstrobilus]] }}
