[[File:Maple leaf Fcb981.JPG|thumb|right|upright=0.7|A maple (''[[Acer platanoides]]'' leaf is '''[[#palmate|palmate]]''' because the veins radiate out from a central point, like fingers from the palm of a hand.]]
