{{term|term= paripinnate |content= [[paripinnate]] }}
{{defn|defn= Having an even number of leaflets (or [[#pinna|pinnae]]), i.e. terminated by a pair of pinnae as opposed to a single pinna. Compare [[#imparipinnate|imparipinnate]].}}

{{term|term= parthenocarpy |content= [[parthenocarpy]] }}
