{{term|term= pepo }}
{{defn|defn=  type of [[#berry|berry]] formed from an [[Ovary|inferior ovary]] and containing many seeds, usually large with a tough outer skin, for instance, [[pumpkin]], [[cucumber]].}}

{{term|term= perennating |content= [[perennating]] }}
