{{term|term= xerophyte |content= [[xerophyte]] }}
{{defn|defn= A plant generally living in a dry habitat, typically showing xeromorphic or succulent adaptation; a plant able to tolerate long periods of drought. Compare [[#xeromorph|xeromorph]].}}

